Packages 
Package Description
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.common
This package contains all the things, that are used by the daemon and the interface library.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.common.communication
This package implements the communication between the buffer daemon and the GBot interfaces.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.common.util
Here you will find utilities, which are used in the whole project.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon
This package contains the implementation of the buffer daemon.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.drivers  
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.drivers.pacificControl
This driver is used for G2021 Gateway hardware using http for accessing the HW.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.drivers.raspberrypii2cdemo
This driver is used for the hardware on a Raspberry Pi using the I2C interface.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.daemon.drivers.unittest
This driver is used for unit tests.
at.ac.tuwien.infosys.g2021.intf
This package contains the Java interface to the driver layer used in the software-defined gateway G2021.
